OL,5, An immigration official at the Home    
OL,6, Office has been suspended after a BBC  
OL,7, investigation revealed he had been     
OL,8, posting racist content on WhatsApp.    
OL,10,FRob Lewis, an ex-Metropolitan Police   
OL,11,Fofficer, is understood to have created 
OL,12,Fthe group chat, which also included    
OL,13,Fother former Met police officers.      
OL,15,FBBC Newsnight has seen racist messages 
OL,16,Fabout flooding in Pakistan, as well as 
OL,17,FHarry and Meghan, shared in the chat.  
OL,19,FThe Home Office called the messages    
OL,20,F"vile and deplorable".                 
